AIO MInstAll by Andreyonohov & Leha342 Lite on 06/06/2017


In front of you is a light version of November 6, 2017, which has become popular with many users of the latest version of the most frequently used programs from Andrey Onokhov. The image is fitted to the size of a 4.7 Gb DVD.

The process of installing and registering programs and components occurs without user intervention after choosing the required software. The composition of the programs and the changes in this version are shown below.
